# Paste-accident screenshots — the legitimate captures in
# docs/screenshots/ end in a single extension. Files like
# ``foo.png.jpg`` are accidental copies (drag-and-drop save dialogs
# that don't strip the original ext). Curated screenshots are
# tracked individually; this pattern only filters the obvious dupes.
*.png.jpg
*.jpg.png
